## Advanced Examples

### Example 1: Running Statistics

```aria
%STRUCT RunningStats {
    int64:count,
    int64:sum,
    int64:min,
    int64:max
}

int64[]:data = [45, 67, 23, 89, 34, 12, 78];

RunningStats:stats = reduce(data, { 0, 0, INT64_MAX, INT64_MIN }, RunningStats(RunningStats:s, int64:n) {
