## uint64: 64-bit Unsigned Integer

### Range

**Minimum**: 0 (0x0000000000000000)  
**Maximum**: 18,446,744,073,709,551,615 (0xFFFFFFFFFFFFFFFF, 2^64 - 1)  
**Total values**: 2^64

**Approximately**: 18.4 quintillion (18.4 × 10^18)

### Declaration

```aria
