| Feature | `flt32` | `flt64` |
|---------|---------|---------|
| Precision | ~7 digits | ~15 digits |
| Memory | 4 bytes | 8 bytes |
| Speed | Faster | Acceptable |
| Default | ❌ No | ✅ Yes |

