```

---

## Best Practices

### ✅ DO: Group Related Imports

```aria
use std.collections.{
    HashMap,
    HashSet
};
```

### ✅ DO: Use Meaningful Aliases

```aria
use std.collections.HashMap as UserCache;  // ✅ Clear purpose
```

### ✅ DO: Explicit Over Wildcard

```aria
use std.math.{sqrt, abs, pow};  // ✅ Clear what's used
// Not: use std.math.*;
