| Load | ~10-30 cycles | ~3-10 cycles | 1 cycle |
| Store | ~10-30 cycles | ~3-10 cycles | 1 cycle |
| CAS | ~20-50 cycles | ~10-20 cycles | ~5-10 cycles |
| Fence | ~20-40 cycles | ~10-20 cycles | 0 cycles |

