### Stale Detection

```aria
// Arena reallocates (increments generations)
arena.grow(arena.capacity * 2);

// Old handle now stale (generation mismatch)
int32:value = arena.get(h) ? 0;  // Returns 0 (ERR)

// Checking for stale
