int4096:b = 50i4096;

int4096:sum = a + b;       // 150
int4096:diff = a - b;      // 50

// Overflow detection
int4096:max = MAX_INT4096;
int4096:overflow = max + max;  // ERR sentinel

if (overflow == ERR) {
    stderr.write("Overflow in 4096-bit arithmetic!\n");
    !!! ERR_OVERFLOW_4096;
}
```

### Multiplication

```aria
int4096:a = 100i4096;
int4096:b = 50i4096;

int4096:product = a * b;  // 5000 (low 4096 bits)

// ⚠️ WARNING: Full product is 8192 bits!
