```

### Division & Modulo

```aria
int4096:dividend = 100i4096;
int4096:divisor = 50i4096;

// Signed division/modulo (default)
int4096:quotient = dividend / divisor;   // 2
int4096:remainder = dividend % divisor;  // 0

// Unsigned variants (explicit runtime calls)
int4096:u_quotient = aria_lbim_udiv4096(&dividend, &divisor);
int4096:u_remainder = aria_lbim_umod4096(&dividend, &divisor);

// Division by zero
int4096:zero = 0i4096;
int4096:bad = dividend / zero;  // ERR sentinel

if (bad == ERR) {
    !!! ERR_DIVISION_BY_ZERO;
}
```

