## Example: RSA-8192 Key Validation

```aria
// Verify RSA-8192 key parameters
// n = p × q (where p, q are 4096-bit primes, but we can check with int2048 ops)

int2048:p_low = extract_low_2048_bits(rsa_prime_p);
int2048:q_low = extract_low_2048_bits(rsa_prime_q);

