### Ascending Order

```aria
func:ascending = int64(int64:a, int64:b) {
    pass(a <=> b);
};

int64[]:data = [42, 17, 99, 3, 56];
sort(data, ascending);
// data = [3, 17, 42, 56, 99]
```

### Descending Order

```aria
func:descending = int64(int64:a, int64:b) {
    pass(b <=> a);  // Reverse comparison
};

int64[]:data = [42, 17, 99, 3, 56];
sort(data, descending);
// data = [99, 56, 42, 17, 3]
```

