## Implementation Note

```aria
// Typical implementation keeps first occurrence
fn unique(arr: []T) -> []T {
    seen: set<T> = {};
    Result: []T = [];

    till(arr.length - 1, 1) {
        when not seen.contains(arr[$]) then
            result.append(arr[$]);
            seen.insert(arr[$]);
        end
    end

    return result;
}
```

