### Common Type Combinations

| Result Type | Use Case | Example |
|-------------|----------|---------|
| `Result<T, int8>` | Simple error codes (0-255) | File I/O, parsing, validation |
| `Result<T, string>` | Descriptive error messages | User-facing errors, debugging |
