## Guard Clauses

```aria
fn withdraw(amount: f64) -> bool {
    // Guard clauses - check error conditions first
    if amount <= 0 {
        stderr << "Amount must be positive\n";
        return false;
    }

    if amount > balance {
        stderr << "Insufficient funds\n";
        return false;
    }

    if account_frozen {
