## Common Patterns

### Validation

```aria
if !is_valid_email(email) {
    fail "Invalid email format";
}
```

### Range Checking

```aria
if value < min || value > max {
    fail "Value out of range";
}
```

### Null/Nil Checking

```aria
user: User? = find_user(id);

if user == nil {
    fail "User not found";
}

// Safe to use user here
