## Type Parameter Order

Convention: **Most important/used first**:

```aria
// Good: Data type first, error type second
enum Result<T, E> {
    Ok(T),
    Err(E)
}

// Good: Key first, value second
struct Map<K, V> { }

// Good: Input first, output second
