### Swap Values

```aria
fn swap(a: &i32, b: &i32) {
    temp: i32 = a;
    a = b;
    b = temp;
}

x: i32 = 10;
y: i32 = 20;
swap($x, $y);
stdout << x << ", " << y;  // 20, 10
```

