---

## Reborrowing

Can create new borrow from existing:

```aria
fn modify(value: &i32) {
    helper($value);  // Reborrow as mutable
}

fn helper(v: &i32) {
    v = v * 2;
}
```

---

## Best Practices

### ✅ DO: Use When Modification Needed

```aria
