```

---

## Slice Patterns

```aria
// ✅ Idiomatic
match items {
    [] => stdout << "empty",
    [x] => stdout << "one: $x",
    [x, y] => stdout << "two: $x, $y",
    [first, ...rest] => stdout << "many, first: $first",
}

