## Best Practices

### ✅ DO: Use for Structured Data

```aria
// Correct: Machine-readable data goes to stddati
config: Config = stddati.read_toml()?;
api_request: JsonValue = stddati.read_json()?;
batch_data: []Record = stddati.read_msgpack()?;
