### ❌ DON'T: Mix with stdin

```aria
// WRONG: Ambiguous - which stream is which?
user_input: string = stdin.read_line();
data: JsonValue = stddati.read_json()?;

// RIGHT: Clearly separate concerns
when interactive_mode then
    user_input: string = stdin.read_line();
else
    data: JsonValue = stddati.read_json()?;
end
```

