// No error handling!

// GOOD: Handle errors
writeFile("log.txt", "data")
    .onError(NIL(Error:err) { logError(err); pass(NIL); });
```

### ❌ Don't Write Sensitive Data Without Protection

```aria
// BAD: Plain text passwords
writeFile("passwords.txt", userPassword);

// GOOD: Encrypt before writing
