## Visibility

### Private by Default

```aria
// math.aria
fn helper() -> i32 {  // Private
    return 42;
}

pub fn public_fn() -> i32 {  // Public
    return helper();
}
```

### Public Items

```aria
pub fn function() { }       // Public function
pub struct Data { }         // Public struct
pub const MAX: i32 = 100;   // Public constant
```

---

## Re-exports

```aria
