## Coroutine Methods

```aria
fn* example() -> i32 {
    yield 1;
    yield 2;
    yield 3;
}

fn main() {
    coro = example();

    // Get next value
    value: ?i32 = coro.next();

    // Check if done
    done: bool = coro.is_done();

    // Reset to start
    coro.reset();

    // Send value to coroutine
    coro.send(42);
}
```

