## Best Practices

### ✅ DO: Group Related Values

```aria
// Good
pick status_code {
    case 200, 201, 204:
        handle_success();
    case 400, 404, 422:
        handle_client_error();
    case 500, 503:
        handle_server_error();
}
```

### ✅ DO: Use Ranges for Continuous Values

```aria
// Good
pick age {
    case 0..=12:
        category = "child";
    case 13..=17:
        category = "teen";
    case 18..=64:
        category = "adult";
    else:
        category = "senior";
}
```

### ❌ DON'T: Duplicate Cases

```aria
// Wrong
pick value {
    case 1:
        a();
    case 1:  // Error: Duplicate!
        b();
}
```

### ❌ DON'T: Have Unreachable Cases

```aria
// Wrong
pick value {
    case _:  // Catches everything
        handle_all();
    case 1:  // Never reached!
        handle_one();
}
```

