## Advanced Examples

### Example 1: Nested Transformation

```aria
int64[][]:matrix = [[1, 2], [3, 4], [5, 6]];

// Double all elements in 2D array
int64[][]:doubled = transform(matrix, int64[](int64[]:row) {
    pass(transform(row, int64(int64:n) { pass(n * 2); })?);
