### Large Factorial

```aria
// Factorial up to ~33
fn factorial(n: i32) -> i128 {
    Result: i128 = 1i128;
    till(n - 2, 1) {
        i: i32 = $ + 2;
        result *= i as i128;
    }
    return result;
}
```

