| **Performance** | ~1.0-1.03× | 1.0× baseline | ≈ (nearly identical) |
| **Safety** | ✅ Defined behavior | ❌ UB minefield | ✅ tbb64 |

### The abs(INT64_MIN) Genomic Bug

```c
