## Advanced Examples

### Example 1: Fibonacci Sequence

```aria
int64:a = 0;
int64:b = 1;

till(10, 1) {
    print(`Fib(&{$}) = &{a}`);
    int64:next = a + b;
    a = b;
    b = next;
}
```

### Example 2: Factorial

```aria
int64:factorial = 1;

till(10, 1) {
    if ($ > 0) {
        factorial *= $;
    }
}
// factorial = 10! = 3628800
```

### Example 3: Prime Number Check

```aria
func:isPrime = bool(int64:n) {
    if (n < 2) { pass(false); }

    bool:prime = true;
    till(n / 2, 1) {
        if ($ > 1 && n % $ == 0) {
            prime = false;
            break;
        }
    }
    pass(prime);
};
```

### Example 4: Nested Grid

```aria
