## Pointer Types

### Raw Pointers

```aria
*void      // void* - pointer to anything
*u8        // char* / uint8_t*
*i32       // int*
*f64       // double*
```

---

### Const vs Mutable

```aria
*const T   // const T* - read-only
*mut T     // T* - mutable
```

---

## Creating Pointers

### Address-of Operator

```aria
value: i32 = 42;
ptr: *i32 = &value;  // Get address of value
```

