### ⚠️ WARNING: Dangling Pointers

```aria
ptr: *i32 = extern.malloc(sizeof(i32));
extern.free(ptr);
value: i32 = *ptr;  // ❌ Use after free!
```

---

### ⚠️ WARNING: Buffer Overruns

```aria
